        header1: 'Content of the online offering',
        paragraph1: 'All of the content in our Web presence is prepared with great care and to the best of our knowledge. However, no guarantee can be assumed that this is up-to-date, complete and correct for all of the sites. In addition, Rota Yokogawa does not assume any guarantee for the 24/7 availability of the information provided on its Web site, nor for the omission of any other technical defects. Any liability claims that are based on material or intellectual damage that are caused by the use or non-use of the information offered, or from the use of incorrect or incomplete information, are generally excluded, to the extent that there was no wilful or grossly negligent behaviour on the part of Rota Yokogawa',
        paragraph1_2:'Rota Yokogawa expressly reserves the right to change parts of the Web site or the entire offering without any special announcement, to supplement this, to delete it, or to temporarily or finally discontinue publication.',
        header2: 'References and links',
        paragraph2_1: 'This Web site also includes correspondingly marked links or references to third-party Web sites as information. Responsibility for this third-party content is solely with this content provider. Rota Yokogawa only provides access for the use of this third-party content.',
        paragraph2_2: 'Rota Yokogawa does not have any statutory obligation to monitor the third-party content provided or stored (Sections 8-10 of the Telemediagesetz - TMG - German Telemedia Act). The first time that a link is created to another Web offering, a review of its content is performed as to whether this could initiate any possible responsibility under the civil or penal codes. However, we are totally unable to influence the current or future design, content or the copyrights to the linked Web sites. Rota Yokogawa expressly distances itself from all of the content of all of the linked Web sites that were changed after the link was placed.',
        paragraph2_3: 'Only the provider of the Web site to which a reference is made is liable for any illegal, incorrect or incomplete content, and in particular for damage that results from the use or non-use of third-party information, and not the party which makes reference to the respective publication via links. This content is removed immediately once we become aware of a concrete legal violation. Rota Yokogawa is not liable before it becomes aware of this fact.',
        header3: 'Copyright and brand rights',
        paragraph3_1: 'If not otherwise stated, all of the Web sites are subject to copyright. This applies in particular to text, images, graphics, audio, video or animated files, including their order on the Web sites. Duplication or use of these Web sites (or parts thereof) in other electronic or printed publications and their publication (including in the Internet) is only permitted after prior approval by Rota Yokogawa. In addition, images, graphics, text or other files may be fully or partially subject to third-party copyrights.',
        paragraph3_2: 'If not otherwise stated, all brands on the Rota Yokogawa Web site are subject to brand protection rights. This applies in particular to brands, type labels, company logos and emblems of Rota Yokogawa and the Yokogawa Group. The brands and design elements used on our Web sites are the Yokogawa Group’s intellectual property. The brands and trademarks protected by third parties are subject, without restriction, to the provisions of the respective applicable brand law and the ownership rights of the respective registered owners.',
        header4: 'Data protection',
        paragraph4: 'See',
        routerlink_privacy: 'Data Protection Statement',
        header5: 'Password, registration',
        paragraph5_1: 'Some pages of the Web site may be password-protected. Only registered users can access these pages in the interests of the security of our business transactions and data protection. You should thus always treat your log-in data confidentially, and close the browser window or mobile application when you have finished the communication with us, in particular if you use the computer or mobile end devices together with other people.',
        paragraph5_2: 'There is no entitlement to registration by Rota Yokogawa. In particular, Rota Yokogawa reserves the right to subject Web sites that were previously freely accessible to a registration requirement. Rota Yokogawa is authorized to revoke the right to access by blocking access data, without having to state reasons, in particular if the user:',
        list_item_1: 'provided incorrect information for registration, or abusively used the used identification,',
        list_item_2: 'violates these terms and conditions of use or his duty of care in dealing with the login-dataviolates these terms and conditions of use or his duty of care in dealing with the login-data, or',
        list_item_3: 'has violated applicable law during access or in using the Web sites.',
        header6: 'Service offerings',
        paragraph6: 'Rota Yokogawa offers optional support and/or services in a specially protected area. This requires users to register and input and update device-specific information and further information using the Yokogawa online platform. Rota Yokogawa notes that confidential information or information protected under ownership law cannot be transferred or provided via this Web site. Accordingly, Rota Yokogawa assumes that all of the documents, information or other contributions or information that you transfer or otherwise provide via this Web site is not confidential and is not protected by copyright or other ownership rights. Rota Yokogawa does not review the information that you provide to ensure that it is feasible, complete or correct. As a result, Rota Yokogawa does not assume any responsibility for transfers or the current nature, completeness or correctness of services provided on this basis, in particular reminder functions for maintenance or service intervals. 24/7, disruption-free operation is not guaranteed. Rota Yokogawa reserves the right to restrict or discontinue the services either in full or in part without prior notice. Customers must ensure that their data is protected. Use is solely the customer’s responsibility.',
        header7: 'Changes to the terms and conditions of use',
        paragraph7: 'Rota Yokogawa reserves the right to change these Terms and Conditions of Use after prior announcement. You will be informed of any such changes in advance. The changes only come into effect after you have accepted them. In the event that you do not accept these changes, both parties can cancel this agreement. The notice period is one month from receipt of notice of the change.',
        current_date:'November 2016',
        print: 'Print'
      },
      Datenschutz: {
        title: 'Data Privacy Statement',
        paragraph0: 'We are very pleased that you have visited our Web site and would like to ensure that you have the very best information - not only for our services, but also about data processing on our Web site. The information below aims to inform you of how we deal with, collect, use and store personal data. We process personal data that is collected during visits to our Web sites in line with German data protection law.',
        header1: 'Responsible Agent',
        paragraph_item1_1: 'Rota Yokogawa GmbH & Co. KG',
        paragraph_item1_2: 'Rheinstr. 8, 79664 Wehr, Germany',
        header2: 'What is personal data?',
        paragraph2: 'Personal data is information that is or could be allocated to you as an individual. This includes, for example, your name, address, telephone number and e-mail address.',
        header3: 'Collecting and processing personal data',
        paragraph3: 'If you visit our Web sites, as a matter of course our Web servers store the IP address that you are allocated by our Internet service provider, the Web site that you visit us from, the Web sites that you visit from our site, as well as the date and duration of your visit. Personal data is only saved if you provide this voluntarily, e.g., as part of a registration, a survey, a price tender or to execute an agreement',
        header4: 'Use and transmission of personal data and designated purpose',
        paragraph4: 'Rota Yokogawa uses your personal data for the technical administration of the Web sites, for customer management, for product surveys and for marketing, only to the extend required for these respective purposes. Personal data will only be transferred to government institutions and authorities according to mandatory national legal requirements. Our employees, agencies and merchants are subject to non-disclosure agreements with us.',
        header5: 'Online registration portal',
        paragraph5_1: 'As a rule, you do not have to provide any personal data to access our Web sites. However, you may provide personal data in order to use online communication services. Any such data that you provide via the online registration portal concerning your person (e.g. name, address, telephone number, e-mail address, etc.) is only saved if you provide us with this data to use certain services on our Web site (e.g. registration of devices, guarantees/services, use of personalized Web site functions, reminder functions, newsletter registration (e-mail only).',
        paragraph5_2: 'This data is processed and used by u and our affiliated companies in the Yokogawa group of companies worldwide, exclusively in order to provide you with the desired services. In the event that personal data is transferred to Rota Yokogawa companies with their registered offices in countries outside the EU or the EEC (so-called third-party countries), we ensure a reasonable level of data protection via contractual inter-company agreements via the so-called EU standard contractual clauses.',
        paragraph5_3: 'Processing and use of this data for other purposes (e.g., sending additional information about our company and our products, for example by making direct contact) or passing this on to external partner and service companies only takes place if you have expressly authorized this type of use. We ask, if you would like to receive this type of communication. Transferring your personal data to third-parties is also subject to your authorization to the extent that this goes beyond the extent permitted by law.',
        paragraph5_4: 'We use a so-called “double opt-in” system on certain Web sites. That means that we send you a confirmation mail with your registration data after you register for the first time. You then have to use this registration data to access our Web site. Your registration will only be activated after you have registered in this manner using your user name and password. This allows us to ensure that you have given your express permission when you register.',
        header6: 'Cookies',
        paragraph6_1: 'Rota Yokogawa uses cookies in order to track visitors preferences and to thus ensure an optimum Web site design. Cookies are small files that are stored on your hard drive. This makes navigation easier and makes sure that a Web site is very user-friendly. Cookies also help us to identify particularly popular areas in our Internet offering. For example, we can tailor the content of our Web sites more precisely to your needs, and thus improve our offering for you. Cookies can be used to ascertain if there has already been communication with our sites from your computer. Only the cookie on your computer is identified. Personal data can be stored in cookies if you have accepted this, for example to make secure online access easier, so that you do not have to input your user ID and password again.',
        paragraph6_2: 'Of course you can also view our Web site without cookies. Most browsers accept cookies automatically. However you can prevent cookies from being saved on your hard drive by selecting the option *do not accept cookies* in your browser settings. You can delete cookies that have already been set on your computer at any time. Please check your browser instructions to find out how. However, if you do not accept cookies, this may lead to restrictions in the functionality of our offerings.',
        header7: 'Security',
        paragraph7: 'Rota Yokogawa uses technical and organization security activities to protect your data that we manage against manipulation, loss, damage and access by unauthorized parties. Our security measures are constantly improved in line with technology developments. Our employees undertake not to disclose any data.',
        header8: 'Links to other Websites',
        paragraph8: 'Our Web site includes links to other Web sites. We check the links to external Web sites prior to linking. However, we cannot ensure that their operators uphold data protection requirements. If we become aware of any infringements or legal violations we will remove the corresponding links.',
        header9: 'Right to information',
        paragraph9: 'Upon request, Rota Yokogawa or the agent responsible for you will inform you as quickly as possible, in line with applicable law, as to if and which personal data have been stored about you by our company. If you are registered as a user with us, we also offer you the opportunity to view your data yourself, and to delete or change these if required. If, despite our efforts to ensure correct and current data, incorrect information is stored, we will correct this upon your request.',
        header10: 'Data protection officer for Rota Yokogawa',
        paragraph10: 'If you have any questions regarding the processing of your personal data, you can contact our data protection officer confidentially. Our data protection officer is there to help with any information you may require or comments or criticism that you may have.',
        paragraph_item10_1: 'Rota Yokogawa',
